  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Suzaku Clan, level 16+, Phoenix Ascension Clan Feat It may have taken you years, countless hardships, and impossible odds, but you've finally suceeded where countless generations of your clansmen have failed. You have become a true Phoenix.</p><ul><li>Learn the Fire Release: Phoenix Blessing Jutsu. It does not count against your jutsu known.</li><li>For every 5 years that pass, your body only ages 1.</li><li>Whenever you are reduced to 0 HP, your body combusts into a flaming inferno before denoting. All creatures within 10ft of you must make a Dexterity saving throw or be engulfed by the blast taking 10d10 fire damage or half as much on a success. At the start of your next turn, you reconstitute, rising from the ashes regaining quarter of your maximum HP and a quarter of your maximum Chakra or as much as you had prior to being reduced to 0 (whichever is higher), and cleansing yourself of any negative effects or jutsu present when you were reduced to 0. You may only use this feature once per seven long rests.</li></ul>",
